room_title: Escape room "Return of the Paranormal Investigator" by Central Arkansas Escape Rooms in Little Rock
room_address: 108 West F Avenue North Little Rock, AR 72116
room_description:
He's back ... and he's better than ever! Wolf Muldoon, a world-renowned paranormal investigator, is headquartered right here in Central Arkansas. Here is where Wolf keeps his office and checks in with Central Headquarters. Would you like to make an appointment? We keep his schedule and would be happy to set a time for you.
But when you arrive, please be prepared. Mysteries await and his secrets are well hidden. If we escort you to his new office, will you be able to solve the mysteries hidden therein? Or will you remain locked in? Only the best investigators can puzzle their way out!
